e3:["$","$L13a",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":".claude/\n└── rules/\n    ├── typescript.md      ← TypeScript 编码规则\n    ├── testing.md         ← 测试编写规则\n    ├── git-commit.md      ← Git 提交规则\n    └── security.md        ← 安全相关规则\n"}]}]
e4:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":"每个规则文件就是一个普通的 Markdown 文件："}]
e5:["$","$L13a",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"# TypeScript 规则\n\n- 始终启用严格模式\n- 禁止使用 `any`，用 `unknown` 替代\n- Props 用 `interface` 定义，联合类型用 `type`\n- 优先使用类型守卫而非 `as` 断言\n- 枚举用 `const enum` 或字面量联合类型\n"}]}]
e6:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":["不带 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"paths"}]," 限定的规则文件在会话启动时自动加载"]}],"，与 CLAUDE.md 一起注入上下文。带 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"paths"}]," 限定的规则则是",["$","strong",null,{"children":"按需加载"}],"——只有当 Claude 操作匹配路径的文件时才会激活。"]}]
