13:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Claude Code 第五篇：记忆层——CLAUDE.md、Rules 与 Auto Memory | 袁慎建的技术博客"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Claude Code 每次启动都是一张白纸——除非你给它\"记忆\"。CLAUDE.md 是你写给 Claude 的操作手册，Rules 是模块化的规则引擎，Auto Memory 是 Claude 自己的笔记本。三者配合，让 Claude 不再每次都从零开始。本文详解三套记忆系统的机制、写法与实战模式。"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"author","content":"袁慎建"}],["$","link","3",{"rel":"manifest","href":"/manifest.json","crossOrigin":"$undefined"}],["$","meta","4",{"name":"keywords","content":"软件开发,AI 编程,ClaudeCode"}],["$","meta","5",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","meta","6",{"name":"googlebot","content":"index, follow, max-video-preview:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-snippet:-1"}],["$","meta","7",{"name":"theme-color","content":"#000000"}],["$","meta","8",{"name":"color-scheme","content":"dark light"}],["$","link","9",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://yuanshenjian.cn/articles/2026/04/05/claude-code-memory-and-claude-md"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"mobile-web-app-capable","content":"yes"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"apple-mobile-web-app-title","content":"YSJ Blog"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style","content":"default"}],["$","meta","13",{"property":"og:title","content":"Claude Code 第五篇：记忆层——CLAUDE.md、Rules 与 Auto Memory"}],["$","meta","14",{"property":"og:description","content":"Claude Code 每次启动都是一张白纸——除非你给它\"记忆\"。CLAUDE.md 是你写给 Claude 的操作手册，Rules 是模块化的规则引擎，Auto Memory 是 Claude 自己的笔记本。三者配合，让 Claude 不再每次都从零开始。本文详解三套记忆系统的机制、写法与实战模式。 | 阅读约 11 分钟 | 标签: 软件开发, AI 编程, ClaudeCode"}],["$","meta","15",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://yuanshenjian.cn/articles/2026/04/05/claude-code-memory-and-claude-md"}],["$","meta","16",{"property":"og:site_name","content":"袁慎建的技术博客"}],["$","meta","17",{"property":"og:locale","content":"zh_CN"}],["$","meta","18",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://yuanshenjian.cn/images/og-default.webp"}],["$","meta","19",{"property":"og:image:width","content":"1200"}],["$","meta","20",{"pr